  "text": "We use the semismooth Newton method [CITATION_1] to solve the discrete problem (5.3) . We follow a similar argument as [CITATION_2] in this subsection. Since transferring the proofs in [CITATION_3] to our setting is straightforward, we only describe the algorithm and the convergence result.",
